com.bytelightning.opensource.pokerface

Class PokerFaceKeyManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.net.ssl.X509ExtendedKeyManager
      • com.bytelightning.opensource.pokerface.PokerFaceKeyManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    KeyManager, X509KeyManager

    public class PokerFaceKeyManager
extends X509ExtendedKeyManager
    Semi-delegating X509ExtendedKeyManager which always returns it's own 'server' alias, but delegates all other calls.
